'Yohimbine' is a mild MAOI with stimulant and aphrodisiac effects. It is sold as
prescription medicine in pure form for the treatment of sexual dysfunction.
Yohimbine was explored as a remedy for type 2 diabetes in animal and human
models carrying polymorphisms of the Î± 2A -adrenergic receptor
gene.
